00:15:32.820 --> 00:15:35.820 align:middle line:84%
And the physician
handed him a copy

00:15:35.820 --> 00:15:38.550 align:middle line:84%
of "Diet for a New
America," my book,

00:15:38.550 --> 00:15:42.630 align:middle line:84%
not knowing that the John
Robbins who'd written it

00:15:42.630 --> 00:15:46.380 align:middle line:84%
was the son of his patient, Irv
Robbins, the founder and owner

00:15:46.380 --> 00:15:47.700 align:middle line:90%
of Baskin-Robbins.

00:15:47.700 --> 00:15:49.500 align:middle line:84%
And my dad of course
knew, because I'd

00:15:49.500 --> 00:15:54.000 align:middle line:84%
sent him already a copy of the
book, but he didn't tell him.

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:56.700 align:middle line:84%
But he went home, and
now, because the book

00:15:56.700 --> 00:15:59.790 align:middle line:84%
had been blessed by the high
priest of Western medicine,

00:15:59.790 --> 00:16:00.630 align:middle line:90%
he began to read it.

00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:02.370 align:middle line:84%
I'm sure he read the
copy the doctor gave him,

00:16:02.370 --> 00:16:04.328 align:middle line:84%
not the copy I'd sent
him that was autographed.

00:16:04.328 --> 00:16:08.340 align:middle line:84%
But he read it, and he
started to make changes.

00:16:08.340 --> 00:16:10.270 align:middle line:90%
Small ones at first.

00:16:10.270 --> 00:16:11.670 align:middle line:90%
But he got results.

00:16:11.670 --> 00:16:15.310 align:middle line:84%
And then he made more changes,
more results, more changes,

00:16:15.310 --> 00:16:17.440 align:middle line:90%
more results.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:21.480 align:middle line:84%
Fast forward two
years, he's off all

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:23.190 align:middle line:90%
the medications he'd been on.

