00:16:49.530 --> 00:16:51.600 align:middle line:84%
not going to believe
what's happened.

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:52.510 align:middle line:90%
I said, OK.

00:16:52.510 --> 00:16:53.310 align:middle line:90%
What's happened?

00:16:53.310 --> 00:16:55.740 align:middle line:90%
He said, it's unbelievable.

00:16:55.740 --> 00:16:57.480 align:middle line:90%
I said, all right.

00:16:57.480 --> 00:17:00.660 align:middle line:90%
What's unbelievable?

00:17:00.660 --> 00:17:03.930 align:middle line:84%
It's really not possible,
but it's happened.

00:17:03.930 --> 00:17:06.810 align:middle line:90%
What, Dad?

00:17:06.810 --> 00:17:10.560 align:middle line:84%
Well, it turns out
you were right.

00:17:10.560 --> 00:17:15.150 align:middle line:84%
And-- honestly, that my
dad, who had achieved

00:17:15.150 --> 00:17:18.480 align:middle line:84%
this phenomenal
business success,

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:22.170 align:middle line:84%
could say to this son that
rejected his life work that you

00:17:22.170 --> 00:17:25.980 align:middle line:84%
might have been
right, about anything,

00:17:25.980 --> 00:17:31.320 align:middle line:84%
I respect that enormously,
because that's of the heart.

00:17:31.320 --> 00:17:34.050 align:middle line:90%
That takes something.

00:17:34.050 --> 00:17:37.320 align:middle line:90%
This is a man who had it all.

00:17:37.320 --> 00:17:39.450 align:middle line:90%
He was a billionaire.

00:17:39.450 --> 00:17:46.260 align:middle line:84%
And yet, he could say to his
son who walked away from it all

00:17:46.260 --> 00:17:48.840 align:middle line:90%
that you might have been right.

00:17:48.840 --> 00:17:53.820 align:middle line:84%
To me, I will always
live with that joy.

00:17:53.820 --> 00:17:55.750 align:middle line:84%
Then after that, we
had a rapprochement.

00:17:55.750 --> 00:17:57.480 align:middle line:84%
We began to talk
about a lot of things.

00:17:57.480 --> 00:17:59.700 align:middle line:84%
There was a
reconciliation between us,

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:01.620 align:middle line:84%
and our relationship
got completely renewed.

00:18:01.620 --> 00:18:04.240 align:middle line:90%


00:18:04.240 --> 00:18:05.440 align:middle line:90%
The connection was there.

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:06.520 align:middle line:90%
The love was there.

00:18:06.520 --> 00:18:09.550 align:middle line:84%
The respect was there, both
ways, reciprocal, moving.

00:18:09.550 --> 00:18:11.150 align:middle line:90%
And we were connected again.

00:18:11.150 --> 00:18:13.870 align:middle line:84%
And he lived another
20 years, most of them

00:18:13.870 --> 00:18:17.980 align:middle line:84%
very healthy ones, when
the prognosis had been he

00:18:17.980 --> 00:18:19.480 align:middle line:90%
was on his deathbed.

00:18:19.480 --> 00:18:23.560 align:middle line:84%
I disappointed him so
much by making a choice

00:18:23.560 --> 00:18:26.740 align:middle line:84%
that I felt was for integrity,
but from his point of view,

00:18:26.740 --> 00:18:28.850 align:middle line:90%
it was a slap in the face.

00:18:28.850 --> 00:18:33.310 align:middle line:84%
And that, in the end,
I was able to give him

00:18:33.310 --> 00:18:37.270 align:middle line:84%
something perhaps more
valuable than had I

00:18:37.270 --> 00:18:39.200 align:middle line:90%
done the obvious thing.

00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:42.670 align:middle line:84%
And since then, I've
written other books,

00:18:42.670 --> 00:18:46.010 align:middle line:84%
and had sold millions of
copies of them, and had many,

00:18:46.010 --> 00:18:49.690 align:middle line:84%
many people write me and tell
me that their lives had been

00:18:49.690 --> 00:18:52.600 align:middle line:84%
changed in similar
ways to my dad's.

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:58.390 align:middle line:84%
And that is so
much more rewarding

00:18:58.390 --> 00:18:59.980 align:middle line:90%
and fulfilling for me.

00:18:59.980 --> 00:19:07.660 align:middle line:90%


00:19:07.660 --> 00:19:10.000 align:middle line:84%
I think we really need
to redefine success

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:13.500 align:middle line:84%
in a way that includes our
hearts, and includes our love,

00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:16.390 align:middle line:84%
and includes our compassion,
and includes our caring for one

00:19:16.390 --> 00:19:17.350 align:middle line:90%
another.

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:19.570 align:middle line:84%
I think we know when
we're a success when

00:19:19.570 --> 00:19:23.440 align:middle line:84%
our hearts are strong, and
we live with them in a way.

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:25.300 align:middle line:84%
And so our life
reflects our hearts.

00:19:25.300 --> 00:19:29.070 align:middle line:84%
We make choices that
express our love, or caring.

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:31.750 align:middle line:84%
And then that becomes the
defining aspect of who we are.

