00:19:39.960 --> 00:19:43.185 align:middle line:84%
>> I grew up in New Jersey
in a very blue-collar family.

00:19:43.185 --> 00:19:45.613 align:middle line:90%


00:19:45.613 --> 00:19:47.030 align:middle line:84%
My parents got
divorced, and there

00:19:47.030 --> 00:19:49.910 align:middle line:84%
